node.text:
#WEBUYWEDNESDAY
Beverly Hills Car Club continues to be a trusted and top-rated buyer and has been for many years. Check out our thousands of 5-Star Ratings by going to: https://www.alexmanos.com/testimonials/
We buy classic cars in any condition, top dollar paid! We even offer same day payment.
⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
We’d love to talk to you about buying your classic car. Email contact@alexmanos.com with photos and details about selling your classic car today! You can also contact us directly at 877-356-2365
📷 ❤️ Photographed: Here is a beautiful 1953 Jaguar XK120 Roadster featured with matching numbers is available in Carmine Red with a black interior. The vehicle comes equipped with a 4-speed manual transmission, 3 1/2 liter engine, dual carburetors, Tonneau cover, solid wheels, jack, and Jaguar hub caps. A very original British classic that is available for $79,950
Please include your name, email, and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

node.text:
Ferrari’s ‘Second Soul’ - This is what Ferrari Magazine had to say about the yellow Ferrari:
“Yellow is a bit like Ferrari’s second soul: it is the colour of the city of Modena which, together with the black horse inherited from the family of war hero airman Francesco Baracca, it is part of the Ferrari brand, one of the most famous in the world.”
This is your chance to acquire a legendary, highly acclaimed #classic Ferrari!
💛 This desirable color combination 1979 Ferrari 308GTB featured here with 60,153 miles on the odometer is available in Fly Yellow with a sand beige interior.
Key Features: 5-speed manual transmission, air conditioning, power windows, 4-wheel disc brakes, tool kit, and jack. An excellent original blue plate California car that is available only at Beverly Hills Car Club for $69,950
Please include your name, email, and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

soft top, boot, and white line tires. An excellent and well taken care of 60s American classic that is available for $36,500
Please include your name, email, and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

✅ This American classic is available for $67,500
Please include your name|email and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

#FERRARIFRIDAY
Fun Ferrari Fact:
The 328 has been described as one of the most usable classic Ferraris because of its durable road record, history of appreciating value, and classical aesthetics! 💚
Featured here is a 1986 Ferrari 328GTS in an extremely desirable and sought-after factory color combination of Verde Scuro Metallic (color code #603/C) with a chocolate interior.
- 58,144 miles on the odometer
- Clean Carfax
Key Features: 5-speed manual transmission, air conditioning, power windows, 4-wheel disc brakes, jack, and tool kit. 
✅ A gorgeous color combination Ferrari that is ready to be driven and enjoyed. Do not miss your chance to jump into the ownership of this amazing Italian sports car that is available for $89,950
Please include your name|email and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.

node.text:
#DidYouKnow The ‘T’ stands for Touring and was first applied to the 1968 911T! 💚
This amazing and highly collectible 1971 Porsche 911T Targa featured with matching numbers is available in its factory color combination of Green Metallic with a black interior.
Key Features: 4-speed manual transmission, Weber carburetors, headrest, chrome rocker panels, leather-wrapped steering wheel,
4-wheel disc brakes, Fuchs wheels, jack, and spare tire. Also included with this vehicle are service documents and receipts dating
from 1980 to 2013 totaling over $11,000. A very clean and presentable 911T Targa that is available for $76,500
Please include your name|email and mobile number when sending a DM and we will be in touch very soon.
